title: Live: Russia says its forces downed 118 Ukrainian drones overnight
description: Russian air defences shot down 118 Ukrainian drones overnight, including 52 over the Belgorod region bordering Ukraine, Russian news agencies reported on Thursday. Moscow earlier warned it would make no big concessions on a peace plan for Ukraine after a leaked recording of a call involving US envoy Steve Witkoff showed he had advised the Kremlin on how to pitch a deal to President Donald Trump. Follow our liveblog for the latest updates.
